The manga is really great but it's such a bad translating quality!!! Some translations are just by the translator's individual imagination. For example, P.17, Ichinose's word was not "I'll let you do it until you're satisfied", but "Can you satisfy me?" (私を満足させてくれる?) And P.25, she didn't say "You can cum inside" but "You can decide where you cum by yourself" (どこに射精するか自分で決めて). The fatal wrong translation is that the MC's name (surname) is KAKUTA (角田) but not KANDA (神田)!! Also MC calls the girl her given name "Ichika" (一夏) but not her surname "Ichinose" (一ノ瀬), which the guy she rejected at the beginning called, as well as MC has never used "-sama" but just "-san" (Ichika-san). It's hard to understand how the translator can even get characters' names wrong. I doubt the translator really understands Japanese as well as enough to be in charge of translating mangas.
